Short-only scalping strategy for XAUUSD on the 15-second timeframe. Entries trigger on a fast/slow EMA crossunder near dynamic swing resistance levels. Exits are managed with ATR-based stop loss and take profit.
Session filter restricts trading to 7:00–11:00 AM New York time (ET), covering the NY open — automatically adjusts for EST/EDT. A cooldown prevents back-to-back trades on the same swing.
Settings: EMA 9/21 | Pivot lookback 5 | SL 0.8x ATR | TP 2.0x ATR | Cooldown 12 bars
Release Notes
Micro Rejection Scalping v6 — XAUUSD 15s
Short-only scalping strategy for XAUUSD on the 15-second timeframe. Entries trigger on a fast/slow EMA crossunder near dynamic swing resistance levels. Exits are managed with ATR-based stop loss and take profit.
Session filter restricts trading to 7:00–11:00 AM New York time (ET), covering the NY open — automatically adjusts for EST/EDT. A cooldown prevents back-to-back trades on the same swing.
Settings: EMA 9/21 | Pivot lookback 5 | SL 0.8x ATR | TP 2.0x ATR | Cooldown 12 bars
